  "remarks": "\nIRGC-ASF SSJO is an involved person  within the meaning of the Russia (Sanctions) (EU Exit) Regulations 2019 as it is or has been involved in destabilising Ukraine or undermining or threatening the territorial integrity, sovereignty, or independence of Ukraine in that it has been providing or making available goods or technology that could contribute to destabilising Ukraine or undermining or threatening the territorial integrity, sovereignty or independence of Ukraine.  \n",
